In this task, we are required to scrape a minimum hundred URLs. The URL will be in format of "https://www.amazon.{country}/dp/{asin}". The country code and Asin parameters are in the CSV file "https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1BZSPhk1LDrx8ytywMHWVpCqbm8URT xTJrIRkD7PnGTM/edit?usp=sharing". The CSV file contains 1000 rows. We have used Selenium to Scarpe the following details from the page:-

Product Title
Product Image URL
Price of the Product
Product Details If any URL throws Error 404 then print the {URL} not available and skip that URL.
